room_title: Escape room "Midnight in Morocco" by The Room - Hutchinson in Hutchinson
room_description: President Amad Makbar has "borrowed" the very rare jewel known as "The Heart of the Desert"! Your mission is to recover the jewel so we can return it to its rightful owner. You have one hour to decipher the clues, solve the riddles and retrieve the stone before he returns.
